Name:		ACS
Version:	2016.10
Release:	1%{?dist}
Summary:	ACS CB for CentOS 7	
License:	LGPL
URL:		http://acs-community.github.io/
Source0:	%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz 
Source1:	https://raw.githubusercontent.com/tmbdev/pylinda/master/linda/doc/pythfilter.py

BuildArch: x86_64 aarch64
